ed_anomaly': 'Please analyze the abnormal event between 2025-06-17T21:10:07Z and 2025-06-17T21:28:07Z and provide the root cause.', 'time_range': '2025-06-17 21:10:07+00:00 to 2025-06-17 21:28:07+00:00'}\n\n--- Node Pod Mapping ---\n{'aiops-k8s-01': ['checkoutservice-1', 'recommendationservice-2', 'productcatalogservice-2', 'frontend-1', 'shippingservice-0', 'emailservice-1'], 'aiops-k8s-02': [], 'aiops-k8s-03': ['recommendationservice-1', 'adservice-0', 'shippingservice-2'], 'aiops-k8s-04': ['paymentservice-2', 'currencyservice-0', 'checkoutservice-0', 'frontend-0'], 'aiops-k8s-05': ['cartservice-1', 'paymentservice-1', 'checkoutservice-2'], 'aiops-k8s-06': ['productcatalogservice-1', 'emailservice-2'], 'aiops-k8s-07': ['adservice-1', 'shippingservice-1', 'emailservice-0', 'currencyservice-1', 'cartservice-0'], 'aiops-k8s-08': ['redis-cart-0', 'recommendationservice-0', 'productcatalogservice-0', 'paymentservice-0', 'frontend-2', 'currencyservice-2', 'checkoutservice-2', 'cartservice-2', 'adservice-2', 'checkoutservice-1']}\n\n\n[ANALYSIS STATE]\n\nCurrent Hypothesis: None\n\nCurrent Iteration: 2\n\n\n[AGENT FINDINGS HISTORY]\n\n--- Log Agent Findings ---\n基于获取到的日志数据，我已经完成了分析。以下是详细的分析结果：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"SUPPORT\",\n  \"detected_log_keys\": [\"PD server timeout\", \"start timestamp may fall behind safe point\", \"Error 9001 (HY000)\", \"rpc error\", \"timeout\", \"failed to query product\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"productcatalogservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"PD server timeout导致数据库查询失败，表现为Error 9001 (HY000)和start timestamp may fall behind safe point错误\",\n      \"evidence\": \"productcatalogservice日志显示：'failed to query product by id: Error 9001 (HY000): PD server timeout: start timestamp may fall behind safe point'\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"由于productcatalogservice的PD server timeout错误，导致前端服务无法获取产品信息，出现rpc error和timeout\",\n      \"evidence\": \"frontend日志显示：'could not retrieve product: rpc error: code = Unknown desc = Error 9001 (HY000): PD server timeout: start timestamp may fall behind safe point'\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n## 分析总结\n\n**根因分析**：\n- **主要根因**：`productcatalogservice` 服务的数据库连接出现 PD (Placement Driver) 服务器超时问题\n- **错误模式**：所有错误都指向同一个核心问题 - `Error 9001 (HY000): PD server timeout: start timestamp may fall behind safe point`\n- **影响范围**：所有 `frontend` 实例都受到影响，无法正常获取产品信息\n\n**关键发现**：\n1. **productcatalogservice** 是问题的源头，其数据库查询失败导致连锁反应\n2. **frontend** 服务作为受害者，因为无法从 productcatalogservice 获取产品数据而报错\n3. 错误模式高度一致，所有错误日志都包含相同的 PD server timeout 错误信息\n4. 问题发生在多个节点上，说明是系统级的问题而非单点故障\n\n**建议**：需要进一步检查 TiDB 集群的 PD 组件状态和数据库连接配置，解决 PD server timeout 问题。\n\n--- Metric Agent Findings ---\n基于获取到的指标数据，我将对故障期间（2025-06-17T21:10:07Z 到 2025-06-17T21:28:07Z）的异常进行分析。\n\n## 分析结果\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"SUPPORT\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\"server_error_ratio\", \"error_ratio\", \"rrt_max\", \"failed_query_ops\", \"pod_processes\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"frontend服务的三个实例（frontend-0、frontend-1、frontend-2）均出现显著的server_error_ratio和error_ratio异常，同时rrt_max指标显示响应时间大幅增加\",\n      \"evidence\": \"frontend-0: server_error_ratio从0%升至9.24%，rrt_max从145308ms降至68753ms；frontend-1: server_error_ratio从0%升至12.08%，rrt_max从211106ms降至93791ms；frontend-2: server_error_ratio从0%升至12.8%，rrt_max从237388ms降至126310ms\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"tidb-tidb\",\n      \"reason\": \"tidb-tidb服务出现failed_query_ops异常，从0次/秒激增至459.34次/秒，同时内存使用率下降30%\",\n      \"evidence\": \"failed_query_ops从0.0激增至459.34，memory_usage从900MB降至663MB，变化率30.33%\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"adservice-2\",\n      \"reason\": \"adservice-2的pod_processes指标显示进程状态异常，p99值从2.0降至1.0，变化率66.67%\",\n      \"evidence\": \"pod_processes的p99值从2.0降至1.0，表明可能存在进程重启或异常终止\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n## 主要发现\n\n1. **前端服务异常**：三个frontend实例均出现严重的错误率上升（9.24%-12.8%），同时响应时间大幅下降，表明可能存在服务降级或故障转移。\n\n2. **数据库故障**：tidb-tidb服务出现大量查询失败（failed_query_ops激增），内存使用率下降，表明数据库层面存在问题。\n\n3. **广告服务进程异常**：adservice-2的进程状态发生变化，可能存在重启或异常终止。\n\n这些异常指标相互关联，前端服务的错误率上升可能与后端数据库查询失败有关，形成了完整的故障链。\n\n--- Trace Agent Findings ---\n基于获取到的调用链数据，我将对异常事件进行详细分析。从trace数据可以看出，这是一个典型的数据库连接问题导致的级联故障。\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"SUPPORT\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\"rrt_max\", \"error_ratio\", \"productcatalogservice->tidb\", \"frontend->productcatalogservice\", \"checkoutservice->productcatalogservice\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"TiDB数据库\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio\",\n      \"evidence\": \"PD server timeout: start timestamp may fall behind safe point错误，出现频次高达161-918次，影响所有调用productcatalogservice的服务\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"productcatalogservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\", \n      \"evidence\": \"GetProduct操作从正常10秒延迟到异常11.5-14.2秒，延迟倍数1.15-1.42倍，表明下游数据库响应变慢\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend服务\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio\",\n      \"evidence\": \"HTTP 500错误频发（436-871次），是productcatalogservice数据库超时的直接受害者\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"checkoutservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio\",\n      \"evidence\": \"PlaceOrder操作失败，错误信息显示无法获取产品信息，表明依赖的productcatalogservice不可用\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n**根因分析总结：**\n\n1. **根本原因**：TiDB数据库出现PD server timeout错误，导致数据库响应变慢甚至不可用\n2. **影响路径**：`TiDB → productcatalogservice → frontend/checkoutservice → 用户请求`\n3. **关键指标**：\n   - 数据库错误率激增（PD timeout错误）\n   - productcatalogservice响应时间增加15-42%\n   - frontend服务500错误率显著上升\n   - checkout流程因产品信息获取失败而中断\n\n这是典型的数据库级联故障模式，TiDB的PD组件超时是整个系统异常的根源。\n\n--- Previous Consensus Decision ---\nNo consensus yet", "metric_analysis_findings": "See Log Findings for Full Context", "trace_analysis_findings": "See Log Findings for Full Context", "consensus_decision": "AGREED", "current_hypothesis": "TiDB数据库PD组件超时是根因，导致productcatalogservice查询失败，进而影响frontend和checkoutservice"}
