rror_ratio\",\n      \"evidence\": \"HTTP 500错误频发（436-871次），是productcatalogservice数据库超时的直接受害者\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"checkoutservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio\",\n      \"evidence\": \"PlaceOrder操作失败，错误信息显示无法获取产品信息，表明依赖的productcatalogservice不可用\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n**根因分析总结：**\n\n1. **根本原因**：TiDB数据库出现PD server timeout错误，导致数据库响应变慢甚至不可用\n2. **影响路径**：`TiDB → productcatalogservice → frontend/checkoutservice → 用户请求`\n3. **关键指标**：\n   - 数据库错误率激增（PD timeout错误）\n   - productcatalogservice响应时间增加15-42%\n   - frontend服务500错误率显著上升\n   - checkout流程因产品信息获取失败而中断\n\n这是典型的数据库级联故障模式，TiDB的PD组件超时是整个系统异常的根源。\n\n--- Previous Consensus Decision ---\nNo consensus yet\n\n--- Metric Agent Findings ---\nSee Log Findings for Full Context\n\n--- Trace Agent Findings ---\nSee Log Findings for Full Context\n\n--- Previous Consensus Decision ---\nAGREED", "log_analysis_findings": "See Hypotheses Summary for Full Context", "metric_analysis_findings": "See Hypotheses Summary for Full Context", "trace_analysis_findings": "See Hypotheses Summary for Full Context", "report_analysis_findings": {"uuid": "0a9fce75-340", "component": "tidb-pd", "reason": "PD server timeout and start timestamp may fall behind safe point causing database query failures", "reasoning_trace": [{"step": 1, "action": "LogSearch(tidb-pd)", "observation": "Found Error 9001 (HY000): PD server timeout: start timestamp may fall behind safe point in productcatalogservice logs"}, {"step": 2, "action": "LoadMetrics(tidb-tidb)", "observation": "failed_query_ops increased from 0 to 459.34, memory_usage dropped 30% indicating database stress"}, {"step": 3, "action": "TraceAnalysis(0a9fce75-340)", "observation": "productcatalogservice GetProduct calls show PD timeout errors affecting frontend and checkoutservice"}]}, "report_analysis_completed": true}
